WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.225
=Episode 16=

00:00:54.525 --> 00:00:56.812
(Treasures Pavilion of Jinzhou
2025 Annual Auction)

00:00:56.812 --> 00:00:57.862
(International Convention Center)

00:00:57.912 --> 00:00:59.479
(Treasures Pavilion of Jinzhou
2025 Annual Auction)

00:00:59.479 --> 00:01:00.159
This one's good.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:02.079
This is great.

00:01:04.090 --> 00:01:05.000
Pretty handsome, right?

00:01:05.662 --> 00:01:06.103
Yeah.

00:01:06.775 --> 00:01:08.280
Then again, it's scorching hot today.

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.240
Why bring me here?

00:01:09.719 --> 00:01:10.662
We had to.

00:01:10.812 --> 00:01:13.280
It's a big collectors' event.

00:01:13.660 --> 00:01:15.060
We're here to broaden our horizons.

00:01:15.110 --> 00:01:17.130
Just look around
even if we can't afford anything,

00:01:19.290 --> 00:01:20.475
Looks like it's going to rain.

00:01:20.475 --> 00:01:23.037
(International Convention Center)

00:01:29.787 --> 00:01:31.254
Welcome, distinguished guests.

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.359
Ye Chen?

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:37.780
You've got some nerve sneaking
into Treasures Pavilion.

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:39.239
I snuck in?

00:01:41.030 --> 00:01:42.362
Let me explain something to you.

00:01:42.719 --> 00:01:43.537
Treasures Pavilion

00:01:43.590 --> 00:01:44.637
is the largest trading hall

00:01:44.637 --> 00:01:46.000
under the Song family.

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:48.587
Only big corporations
and powerful families like ours

00:01:48.587 --> 00:01:49.519
get invited.

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:51.239
Who do you think you are?

00:01:51.319 --> 00:01:52.000
Exactly.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.400
Even the Xiao family
didn't receive an invitation.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:57.599
I only got in
because of Aodong's connections.

00:01:57.662 --> 00:02:00.162
And you two think
you're qualified to get an invitation?

00:02:00.162 --> 00:02:01.561
Yours must be fake.

00:02:01.719 --> 00:02:02.480
Or stolen.

00:02:02.599 --> 00:02:03.719
You're both wrong.

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:05.280
Actually, I bought mine

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.599
from a scalper outside the door.

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:07.640
Satisfied now?

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:09.239
Are you messing with me?

00:02:09.239 --> 00:02:09.840
Let me see it.

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:13.000
Are you even crazier than your sister?

00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:13.519
Hey!

00:02:15.240 --> 00:02:15.879
Security!

00:02:16.100 --> 00:02:17.660
You guys are just going to let him in?

00:02:18.719 --> 00:02:19.120
Sir,

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:21.879
I need to verify your identities.

00:02:22.879 --> 00:02:23.439
Why?

00:02:24.039 --> 00:02:24.400
What?

00:02:24.719 --> 00:02:25.680
Why?

00:02:26.479 --> 00:02:27.800
If you don't cooperate,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:29.560
I'll have someone throw you out.

00:02:30.039 --> 00:02:30.879
Go ahead and try.

00:02:31.790 --> 00:02:32.420
Throw them out.

00:02:32.639 --> 00:02:33.479
Wait a minute.

00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:40.300
(Song Wanting,
eldest daughter of the Song family)

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:42.960
Miss Song.

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:46.039
Everyone here is a distinguished guest.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:48.025
Why are you only checking his identity?

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:52.319
I...

00:02:54.199 --> 00:02:55.039
Mr. Qin said

00:02:55.039 --> 00:02:56.199
they might have a problem.

00:02:56.639 --> 00:02:57.360
These invitations

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:58.319
are very important.

00:02:58.639 --> 00:02:59.400
Shady people

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:00.840
like them

00:03:01.039 --> 00:03:01.879
shouldn't be let in.

00:03:02.919 --> 00:03:04.400
Mr. Qin, since when do you

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.639
get to question
the rules of Treasures Pavilion?

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:10.599
It was her.

00:03:11.580 --> 00:03:12.319
She questioned it.

00:03:12.600 --> 00:03:13.780
It has nothing to do with me.

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:14.280
I...

00:03:14.690 --> 00:03:15.319
Throw them out!

00:03:15.770 --> 00:03:16.360
Throw them out!

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:18.080
Aodong! Aodong!

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:18.479
Get out!

00:03:18.639 --> 00:03:19.080
Aodong!

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.390
You too. Don't bother coming back.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:24.159
I...

00:03:27.159 --> 00:03:27.759
Let's go!

00:03:38.560 --> 00:03:39.199
Thank you.

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:41.120
Mr. Ye, right?

00:03:41.520 --> 00:03:43.000
I'm very sorry for the trouble today.

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:45.000
Hope you walk away
with a great find today.

00:04:00.212 --> 00:04:01.062
(Treasures Pavilion of Jinzhou
2025 Annual Auction)

00:04:01.319 --> 00:04:03.325
I've already suppressed it for now.

00:04:03.412 --> 00:04:05.252
It's completely under control,
so don't worry.

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:07.319
As soon as we get the treasure,

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:09.599
I'll perform a ritual to exorcise
and seal it properly.

00:04:10.050 --> 00:04:10.759
Dad, stop filming.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:12.800
After we get through this disaster...

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:13.599
This way, please.

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:14.599
Broaden your horizons.

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:16.599
Come on. Alright.

00:04:16.862 --> 00:04:18.000
Dong, hurry up!

00:04:18.300 --> 00:04:19.120
- Master Yu!
- Dad!

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:20.800
Master,

00:04:21.039 --> 00:04:21.560
you're here.

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:22.319
Oh right!

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:24.399
Ever since you gave me
that wolf-fang talisman,

00:04:24.399 --> 00:04:25.700
I feel like

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:26.925
I'm completely different,

00:04:27.079 --> 00:04:27.700
inside and out.

00:04:29.439 --> 00:04:30.800
- We're fated to meet.
- Yes.

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:32.319
Let me empower another one for you.

00:04:32.319 --> 00:04:32.879
No, it's okay.

00:04:32.879 --> 00:04:33.800
This is a peace talisman

00:04:33.959 --> 00:04:35.680
for safe travels

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:37.360
and a prosperous home.

00:04:39.762 --> 00:04:41.240
What a coincidence, Master Yu.

00:04:41.639 --> 00:04:42.480
We meet again.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.025
How about giving me one too?

00:04:45.879 --> 00:04:47.920
Normally, a peace talisman
from Xuanji Hall

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:49.759
costs 300,000 each.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:52.319
Today I've really seen

00:04:52.439 --> 00:04:54.720
what "like father, like son" means.

00:04:58.680 --> 00:05:01.480
I have always enjoyed doing good

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:02.850
and accumulating virtue.

00:05:03.639 --> 00:05:04.839
Since fate

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:06.120
has brought us together today,

00:05:06.120 --> 00:05:07.439
after the auction ends,

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:11.040
I'll give each of you a peace talisman
to share in the blessing.

00:05:11.040 --> 00:05:12.480
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:13.360
But...

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:14.240
Thank you, Master Yu!

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.319
Not for him.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:17.399
Not for you.

00:05:21.900 --> 00:05:22.759
Distinguished guests.

00:05:22.759 --> 00:05:23.720
Master Yu, this way please.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:25.240
The auction will now officially begin.

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:28.839
First, let us present our opening item.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:31.160
(Pine and Crane Backflow Incense Burne)
Pine and Crane Backflow Incense Burne

00:05:31.160 --> 00:05:31.879
Legend has it

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:35.839
that Emperor Song Shenzong
bestowed this royal treasure upon

00:05:35.839 --> 00:05:37.000
the great poet Su Dongpo.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:40.160
The pure white smoke
flows down the burner

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:41.560
like a cascading waterfall.

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:42.240
Do you like it?

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.240
Of course.

00:05:43.240 --> 00:05:45.839
Amid the swirling smoke,
the cranes look ready to take flight.

00:05:45.839 --> 00:05:46.880
I'll buy it for you later.

00:05:47.120 --> 00:05:48.839
- Alright, sure.
- Please take a look.

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:50.850
Don't cause trouble.

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:53.160
The starting bid is five million.

00:05:53.519 --> 00:05:54.090
Each increment

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:54.959
is 500,000.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.040
Six million.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:57.759
Six point five million.

00:05:58.199 --> 00:05:58.759
Seven mil...

00:06:01.839 --> 00:06:03.990
Are you crazy? What kind
of place do you think this is?

00:06:04.110 --> 00:06:04.879
Stop messing around.

00:06:04.879 --> 00:06:05.920
Didn't you say you like it?

00:06:06.319 --> 00:06:07.519
I like a lot of things!

00:06:07.519 --> 00:06:07.879
You...

00:06:07.879 --> 00:06:09.079
don't do anything.

00:06:09.170 --> 00:06:09.800
Just stay still.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:11.160
Then don't regret it later.

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:12.040
I won't.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.230
- Sorry.
- You scared me to death.

00:06:15.240 --> 00:06:16.990
I've been standing too long,
just stretching a bit.

00:06:18.437 --> 00:06:20.439
Alright, the highest bid on site

00:06:20.439 --> 00:06:22.637
remains 6.5 million from that gentleman.

00:06:23.519 --> 00:06:24.759
Six point five million,

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:25.759
going once.

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:28.120
Six point five million,

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:29.120
going twice.

00:06:29.130 --> 00:06:30.079
It's going twice already.

00:06:30.079 --> 00:06:31.439
Six point five million,

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.079
going three times...

00:06:33.810 --> 00:06:35.399
Sold! Congratulations to this gentleman.

00:06:35.879 --> 00:06:36.920
Congratulations!

00:06:36.920 --> 00:06:37.839
Six point five million.

00:06:37.839 --> 00:06:38.800
- Thank you.
- Congratulations.

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:40.680
Next, let us present the second item.

00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:42.759
An African blue sapphire.

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:45.439
The starting bid is 1.5 million.

00:06:45.439 --> 00:06:46.240
Three million.

00:06:46.759 --> 00:06:47.519
Four million.

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:49.360
Four point five million.

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.079
Hey, why are you bidding again?

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:52.759
Mom likes it.

00:06:52.759 --> 00:06:54.720
But you can't just buy everything!

00:06:54.740 --> 00:06:55.759
What kind of family
do you think we are?

00:06:55.759 --> 00:06:56.480
Five million.

00:06:58.090 --> 00:06:59.120
Five million, going once.

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:02.800
Five million.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.399
What are you eating?

00:07:03.399 --> 00:07:03.759
Going twice.

00:07:03.759 --> 00:07:04.399
Danshen pills.

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.990
For when my heart feels
like it's about to explode.

00:07:07.010 --> 00:07:08.000
I can't take this stress.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:08.959
Five million,

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:09.920
going...

00:07:09.920 --> 00:07:10.399
Six million.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.720
I'd better take another pill.

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:13.437
Alright, Dong.

00:07:14.079 --> 00:07:14.600
Stop bidding.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:15.120
Going once.

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:16.220
Don't let him drag this out.

00:07:16.230 --> 00:07:17.720
The South Sea Golden Pearl
is about to start bidding.

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:19.199
Dad, he just paid six million for this.

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:20.680
- Isn't he just...
- Enough.

00:07:20.680 --> 00:07:21.600
Don't compete with him.

00:07:22.240 --> 00:07:23.319
Why did we come here?

00:07:23.319 --> 00:07:25.439
Six million, going three times.

00:07:25.959 --> 00:07:26.560
Sold!

00:07:26.790 --> 00:07:27.759
Congratulations, Mr. Ye.

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:28.040
Kid,

00:07:28.639 --> 00:07:29.680
are you crazy?

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:30.959
Six million?

00:07:31.600 --> 00:07:32.360
You'll pay it then.

00:07:33.439 --> 00:07:34.199
Don't worry, Dad.

00:07:34.750 --> 00:07:35.879
Someone will cover it for us.

00:07:36.020 --> 00:07:36.840
She's paying for it.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:37.759
You keep playing.

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:38.590
I'm heading back first.

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:39.040
Dad!

00:07:39.519 --> 00:07:40.150
Let me tell you,

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:41.040
you deal

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.120
with the mess you made.

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:42.970
I don't even know you.

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:43.319
Wait.

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:44.839
Dad!

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.439
Ladies and gentlemen,

00:07:46.879 --> 00:07:47.639
next

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:49.800
is the final item

00:07:49.959 --> 00:07:51.360
of this auction,

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:53.759
the South Sea Golden Pearl.

00:07:54.879 --> 00:07:56.600
This South Sea Golden Pearl comes

00:07:56.879 --> 00:07:58.279
from the gold-lipped oyster.

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:59.040
From the inside out,

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:00.290
it is entirely golden in color,

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:02.160
and perfectly round in shape.

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.319
A South Sea Golden Pearl

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.600
of this quality and size

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:06.120
is truly unprecedented.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.560
It is the most valuable item

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:09.199
in today's auction.

00:08:09.199 --> 00:08:10.079
The starting price

00:08:10.519 --> 00:08:11.680
is twenty million.

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:13.079
Forty million.

00:08:13.879 --> 00:08:14.720
Forty million?

00:08:14.900 --> 00:08:15.720
Ladies and gentlemen,

00:08:16.040 --> 00:08:16.839
this golden pearl

00:08:17.199 --> 00:08:18.439
is something I must have.

00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:19.920
I hope everyone here
will kindly give way.

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.160
Mr. Qin,

00:08:22.000 --> 00:08:23.439
that's not very appropriate.

00:08:23.879 --> 00:08:25.262
At auctions like this, the rule

00:08:25.262 --> 00:08:26.762
has always been highest bidder wins.

00:08:27.120 --> 00:08:28.860
It's not
that I don't understand the rules.

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.860
But my daughter Aoxue
has collapsed from illness.

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:32.150
She even fell into a coma this morning.

00:08:32.160 --> 00:08:34.112
I must obtain this pearl to save her.

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:36.920
Of course,

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:39.000
rules are still rules.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.000
If anyone here

00:08:41.600 --> 00:08:43.039
wants to compete with me

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.240
and bid higher,

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:46.039
then please go ahead.

00:08:48.679 --> 00:08:49.480
Forty million,

00:08:49.919 --> 00:08:50.559
going once.

00:08:52.840 --> 00:08:53.519
Forty million,

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:54.799
going twice.

00:08:55.679 --> 00:08:56.480
Forty million,

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:59.159
going three times.

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.120
Sol...

00:09:08.159 --> 00:09:09.080
Fifty million.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.080
Ye Chen, that's enough.

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:15.240
Sixty million.

00:09:15.559 --> 00:09:16.440
Eighty million.

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:18.159
Ye Chen,

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:19.399
are you done yet?

00:09:19.399 --> 00:09:20.320
I've tolerated you for a long time.

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:20.840
Enough!

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:24.759
Ye Chen,

00:09:25.879 --> 00:09:27.200
you can shout any price you want,

00:09:27.639 --> 00:09:29.000
but think carefully,

00:09:29.159 --> 00:09:30.759
do you even have that kind of money?

00:09:34.960 --> 00:09:37.440
Ms. Wang, why don't you introduce yourself
to everyone?

00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:38.879
Hello, everyone.

00:09:39.039 --> 00:09:39.799
I'm Wang Dongxue.

00:09:40.679 --> 00:09:42.440
Today, Mr. Ye Chen

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:44.559
will fully represent Dihao Group

00:09:44.559 --> 00:09:45.960
in this auction.

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:49.039
Dihao Group will fully support all
of his decisions.

00:09:50.799 --> 00:09:51.840
The funds available to him

00:09:52.240 --> 00:09:53.519
have no upper limit.

00:09:57.639 --> 00:09:59.519
Ye Chen, what exactly
are you trying to do?

00:10:00.039 --> 00:10:01.639
Is this your payback on Aoxue?

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:03.720
Mr. Qin, you're overthinking again.

00:10:04.679 --> 00:10:06.159
This has nothing to do with Aoxue.

00:10:06.500 --> 00:10:08.159
Who knows,
you might even thank me later.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:08.600
You...

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:10.200
Young man,

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:12.559
if it's not about Aoxue,

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:15.039
then it must mean

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:19.200
you're deliberately picking a fight
with me.

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:21.879
You guessed right.

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:24.320
Today, I came for you.

00:10:26.690 --> 00:10:27.799
Eighty million, going once.

00:10:28.159 --> 00:10:28.720
Mr. Qin,

00:10:29.279 --> 00:10:31.679
this concerns your daughter's life.

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:33.840
Don't be stingy. Don't hesitate.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:34.830
Go head-to-head with him.

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:36.879
One hundred million.

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:39.720
One hundred million, going once.

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:43.279
One hundred million, going twice.

00:10:44.039 --> 00:10:44.870
One hundred million,

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:47.200
going three times.

00:10:47.799 --> 00:10:48.559
Sold!

00:10:50.679 --> 00:10:51.840
Congratulations, Mr. Qin.

00:10:52.350 --> 00:10:53.559
Your wish has been fulfilled.

00:10:57.912 --> 00:10:58.591
Mr. Qin.

00:11:02.200 --> 00:11:03.159
Your daughter's life

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:04.879
can now be saved.

00:11:05.919 --> 00:11:06.919
Thank you, Master Yu.

00:11:07.950 --> 00:11:09.350
I would also like to thank everyone

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:10.480
for your understanding.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:14.200
Such a large golden pearl!

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.080
Mr. Qin,

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:15.879
may I?

00:11:19.160 --> 00:11:20.600
Isn't anyone going to do something?

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:21.639
Ye Chen...

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.279
Is nobody going to stop him?

00:11:25.039 --> 00:11:26.320
This... this is impossible!

00:11:26.559 --> 00:11:27.519
What impossible?

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:28.639
It's smashed to pieces!

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:30.600
Call the police and have him arrested!

00:11:30.760 --> 00:11:32.240
Everyone else understands it already.

00:11:32.679 --> 00:11:34.120
How come you still don't get it?

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:35.080
Don't get what?

00:11:35.280 --> 00:11:36.360
Did you hear the auctioneer?

00:11:37.159 --> 00:11:39.520
The South Sea Golden Pearl
comes from a gold-lipped oyster.

00:11:39.879 --> 00:11:40.799
From the inside out,

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:41.962
it should be entirely golden.

00:11:42.060 --> 00:11:43.730
So how could there be
white fibers inside?

00:11:50.159 --> 00:11:50.720
You!

00:11:51.410 --> 00:11:52.480
You're selling fake goods!

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:54.660
Treasures Pavilion
has never sold counterfeit items.

00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:56.240
Then how do you explain this?

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:58.159
Shouldn't Treasures Pavilion give us.....

00:11:58.519 --> 00:11:59.987
Give us an explanation?

00:12:00.159 --> 00:12:01.440
With Miss Song's reputation,

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:03.600
I believe she would never commit fraud

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:05.000
and ruin her own future.

00:12:05.887 --> 00:12:08.039
The only possibility
is that somewhere along the way,

00:12:08.039 --> 00:12:09.039
it was switched.

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:10.887
What do you say, Master Yu?

00:12:31.450 --> 00:12:33.938
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:12:34.025 --> 00:12:37.778
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:12:38.238 --> 00:12:43.175
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:12:43.338 --> 00:12:45.625
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:45.938 --> 00:12:48.618
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:49.688 --> 00:12:52.313
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:52.613 --> 00:12:55.625
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:55.825 --> 00:12:58.875
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:58.988 --> 00:13:01.950
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:13:02.218 --> 00:13:05.375
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:09.350
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:13:09.350 --> 00:13:12.213
♪I belong to no one♪

00:13:12.275 --> 00:13:15.725
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:13:15.725 --> 00:13:18.400
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:13:18.400 --> 00:13:24.738
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪